Well developed and maintained office space. 11,475 sq. ft. of office space on three floors. Excellent central location

Owner-user condo in well managed complex.  Great West End location, only 6 blocks east of 170th Street.  Quick access to 170th Street, and the Anthony Henday Drive.  Ample parking available on site plus street parking.  Fibre optics available within the property.

Common.Strapline.Common.Text: Two-Story Condo in Excellent West End Location

Common.LongDescription.Common.Text: Two separately titled condo units; front and rear unit of building that are seamlessly developed into one unit. Fully developed space over two floors with stairway access to second floor.Air conditioned with security system in place (Telsco)  Awning signage with exposure to 100 Avenue (11,900 average annual weekday traffic).  8 parking stalls that can be reserved for unit with additional surface scramble parking available.

Well maintained property located in desirable West Edmonton area. High quality attractive space with efficient layout with numerous recent renovations. The second floor has a lease in place and that main floor is vacant.

Entire Building Available for Sale OR Main Floor Available for Lease. Strategically located in a well established commercial neighborhood of West Edmonton, the property is easily accessible from Stony Plain Road, 178 Street and 170 Street. The area has an attractive mix of amenities including restaurants, shopping, hotels and other services. The main floor of the unit was renovated in 2014, is well laid out and attractively designed. The main floor has an upgraded front entrance with security system, a reception which allows controlled access to the second floor and main floor office space. The remainder of the main floor is comprised of several offices, a glass-walled boardroom, lounge / lunch area, private washrooms and open work area. The second floor is laid out with an open work room, a glass-walled breakout room, kitchen, large offices, and large washrooms with showers. In addition to the extensive interior renovations the roof and HVAC units were replaced in 2013.
